name: Free Pulse Illustration Kit 130+ Assets and Scenes
description:
We are excited to introduce Pulse Illustration Kit!


It is a vector illustration constructor with unique 15 characters and 88 objects. The kit includes Sketch symbols and Figma components which you can combine and create your own story. You can use this illustration library for your next app design, landing page or a pitch deck. It is free for commercial and personal use. No attribution required. Pulse Illustration Kit includes:


• 103+ Illustrations

• 20+ High-Quality Scenes

• Scene Generator

• Compatibility with Illustrator, EPS, Sketch, Figma, SVG, PNG
